  "description": [
    "Deer SpootsThanks minny toimes raypaytd fer th illigist letther ye was afther sindin me th day befure yister day tillin me ahl the news in thot deer auld Jacksonville which the par iv us love so well because the blissid doughbag is lowcated there as its per manent abode Thot same Jacksonville has bin a crool stepmither t me at toimes an roight glad Oi am phin Oi can wurrk a guy fer a pass to lave it fer a while Oi usea to hov a lot of frins there wance but sinse takin oop me lit therary labors divil a wan hov Oi lift barrin sivin or eight who hov ray mainted faitnful in spite iv ahl at timpts iv me inimies t change thim Thin afther careful reflicshun Oi am convinced thot its no use fer sucn small grafters as mesilf an you to kape oop the struggie whin we hov compate wid sich Naypoleons iv graft as J Murdoch an Willie Ringworm J Murdoch as ye well and thurly know has the intoire city council v Jacksonville wurrkin fer him Ahl ue has to do is to put on his wise look an make noise loike Blackstone"
